Package com.google.openbidder.exchange.doubleclick.interceptor

Standard interceptors.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BidRequestDumpInterceptor
    Dumps requests to a file.
    ConfigurableBidInterceptor
    DoubleClick-specific ConfigurableBidInterceptor, adds full support for multisize slots (which cannot be represented by the pure OpenRTB model).
    DoubleClickInterceptorsModule
    Standard DoubleClick interceptors.
    FlashlessBidInterceptor
    Automatically handles Flashless ads.
    RawBidInterceptor
    Bids by matching a "raw" request pattern, and sending a "raw" response.
    SSLBidInterceptor
    Automatically handles SSL-enabled ads.
    VideoBidInterceptor
    Automatically handles Video ads.
